sequenceDiagram
    participant Text as Input Text
    participant Tok as Tokenizer
    participant Emb as Embeddings
    participant Enc as Encoder
    participant Head as Classifier
    participant Out as Output

    Text->>Tok: raw text

    Note over Tok: SentencePiece<br/>vocab = 251K tokens

    Tok->>Emb: input_ids (≤512)

    Note over Emb: Token embeddings<br/>768 dimensions

    Note over Emb: Relative position<br/>256 buckets

    Emb->>Enc: embeddings

    Note over Enc: 12× Transformer blocks<br/>───────────────<br/>Disentangled Attention<br/>12 heads, 768 dim<br/>───────────────<br/>FFN: 768 → 3072 → 768<br/>GELU activation<br/>───────────────<br/>LayerNorm + Dropout

    Enc->>Head: hidden states h ∈ ℝ^(n×768)

    Note over Head: Linear projection<br/>768 → 41 classes

    Head->>Out: logits z ∈ ℝ^(n×41)

    Note over Out: p = softmax(z)<br/>ŷ = argmax(p)<br/>───────────────<br/>41 BIO labels:<br/>20 entities × (B-, I-) + O
